title: Adam Lambert and Demi Lovato Deny Feud Rumor
text:
Comments Adam Lambert and Demi Lovato tweet 'love' to each other after hit with feud rumor. 
There is no bad blood between Adam Lambert and Demi Lovato contrary to the swirling rumor. The " American Idol " alum was reportedly mad with Demi after she replaced him with Nick Jonas as an opening act for her upcoming tour. "Aww I love you all very much. No beef tween @ddlovato & @nickjonas and me. Biz negotiations are complex- why do we care about the #rumors?" Adam clarified on Twitter. Demi quickly added, "Just goes to show how accurate @TMZ really is... I [love] you @adamlambert." Demi Lovato and Nick Jonas have been frequent collaborators since their Disney days. In May, they announced a joint label dubbed Safehouse Records with music executive Phil McIntyre. Demi's new tour with Nick is to support her newly-released studio album " Confident ".
